        <p>Whether you've been running a cycle of performance enhancers or simply want to optimize your hormonal health, understanding Post Cycle Therapy (PCT) is crucial. Done right, PCT helps you maintain your gains and restore natural hormone production.</p>
        
        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-heading); margin: 40px 0 20px; color: var(--color-primary);">What is PCT?</h2>
        <p>Post Cycle Therapy is a protocol designed to help your body restore its natural hormone production after a cycle. The goal is to:</p>
