          <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Restore natural testosterone production</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Minimize muscle loss</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Control estrogen levels</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Support overall recovery</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-heading); margin: 40px 0 20px; color: var(--color-primary);">Why PCT Matters</h2>
        <p>Skipping PCT is one of the biggest mistakes you can make. Without proper recovery support:</p>
        <ul style="margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Muscle Loss</strong> - Low testosterone means your body can't maintain muscle mass</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Fat Gain</strong> - Hormonal imbalance leads to increased fat storage</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Low Energy</strong> - Fatigue, brain fog, and poor motivation</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Mood Issues</strong> - Depression, irritability, and anxiety</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Libido Problems</strong> - Decreased sex drive and performance</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-heading); margin: 40px 0 20px; color: var(--color-primary);">Key PCT Ingredients</h2>
        
        <h3 style="margin: 30px 0 15px;">1. Ashwagandha</h3>
        <p>Reduces cortisol, supports testosterone production, and helps manage stress during recovery.</p>
        
        <h3 style="margin: 30px 0 15px;">2. Tongkat Ali</h3>
        <p>Stimulates natural testosterone production and reduces SHBG for more free testosterone.</p>
        
        <h3 style="margin: 30px 0 15px;">3. DIM (Diindolylmethane)</h3>
        <p>Helps balance estrogen metabolism, preventing estrogen-related side effects.</p>
        
        <h3 style="margin: 30px 0 15px;">4. Zinc & Magnesium</h3>
        <p>Essential minerals for testosterone production and recovery.</p>
        
        <h3 style="margin: 30px 0 15px;">5. Vitamin D3</h3>
        <p>Supports hormone production and overall health during recovery.</p>
        
        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-heading); margin: 40px 0 20px; color: var(--color-primary);">PCT Protocol</h2>
        <p>A typical PCT protocol runs 4-6 weeks:</p>
        <ul style="margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Week 1-2:</strong> Higher doses to kickstart recovery</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Week 3-4:</strong> Maintenance doses</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Week 5-6:</strong> Taper down (optional)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-heading); margin: 40px 0 20px; color: var(--color-primary);">Lifestyle During PCT</h2>
        <p>Maximize your PCT results with these tips:</p>
        <ul style="margin: 20px 0; padding-left: 25px;">
          <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Sleep 8+ hours</strong> - Crucial for hormone production</li>
          <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Reduce training volume</strong> - Focus on maintaining, not gaining</li>
